data.title: Students Named to the Trustees’, President’s, and Dean’s Lists
data.text:
Please join us in congratulating the students who were named to Champlain College’s honors lists for the Fall 2020 semester.

We are incredibly proud to honor the following students who were named to the Trustees’, President’s, and Dean’s Lists last semester. The global pandemic added unprecedented challenges for everyone, and many of the students listed here also juggle academics with serious jobs, internships, clubs, and volunteering. We hope everyone named to these honors lists takes pride and joy in this tremendous achievement.

Please note: students must be enrolled full time (12 credits or more per semester) in an undergraduate program to be considered for the Dean’s, President’s, and Trustees’ lists.
